question: Indian Air Force(IAF) recently successfully test-fired which missile in Andhra Pradesh during the Combat Guided Weapons Firing 2020?
explanation: Indian Air Force(IAF) recently successfully test-fired Akash missile in Andhra Pradesh during the Combat Guided Weapons Firing 2020 with the purpose to destroy enemy planes. It has been upgraded before testing. It is the India's first indigenously produced medium range Surface to Air missile that can engage multiple targets.
